{
  "page": "Lord of Sandstone",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lord of Sandstone</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> is a title held by the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Qorgyle\" title=\"House Qorgyle\">House Qorgyle</a>, the ruler of <a href=\"/index.php/Sandstone\" title=\"Sandstone\">Sandstone</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dorne.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Dorne and the location of Sandstone\"><img alt=\"Dorne and the location of Sandstone\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/Dorne.png/400px-Dorne.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"191\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/Dorne.png/600px-Dorne.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f5/Dorne.png/800px-Dorne.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 75%; left: 18.9%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 10px; font-size: 10px;\"><img alt=\"Dorne and the location of Sandstone\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Sandstone\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/15px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/20px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 80%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Sandstone</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> and the location of Sandstone\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Sandstone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Gareth_(maester)\" title=\"Gareth (maester)\">Gareth</a>'s <i><a href=\"/index.php/Red_Sands\" title=\"Red Sands\">Red Sands</a></i>, Lord Qorgyle arranged the murder by scorpion of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Tyrell_(lord)\" title=\"Lyonel Tyrell (lord)\">Lyonel Tyrell</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Conquest_of_Dorne\" title=\"Conquest of Dorne\">Conquest of Dorne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Lords_of_Sandstone\">Known Lords of Sandstone</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Sandstone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Lords of Sandstone\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Lord Qorgyle ruling during the Conquest of Dorne.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_daeron_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Quentyn_Qorgyle\" title=\"Quentyn Qorgyle\">Quentyn Qorgyle</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Sandstone&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></